			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Debug Book - Go To Region - Act 3 - WYR - Audience Hall\r\nApproach the group\r\nAn interactive dialog will be started after which Gortash will go to a private place.\r\nTalk to him. After the dialog he will go to his default pos.\r\nWalk away / cast invisibility on yourself and observe the ceremony.\r\nWait more, after the ceremony is done they will start this group dialog."
				},
